ormal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T16:00:23.000Z","msg":"係電腦個地同埋個5v唔靚<br />\nUsb 個電係電腦火牛比, 大多係switching power, 5v dc 其實唔靚<br />\n另外電腦內電子野多, 仲係共地, 好多會野響到個 grounding<br />\nUsb 咪係攞一電腦電而且咪內置ADC, 但大多usb mic 都唔會係有濾波, 從而影響質素<br />\n買個外置interface , 獨立比電<br />\n而且可以用更加好嘅mic"},{"pid":"81912a09cd94258203ff3eb82801441eb523be5d","tid":600345,"uid":63150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T16:02:28.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://us.focusrite.com/usb-audio-interfaces/scarlett-2i2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fus.focusrite.com%2Fusb-audio-interfaces%2Fscarlett-2i2&d=WqTtVrWfq%2BIAU1dwJNkwQePnIAwyWqphGIcg0J4V%2Buw%3D&h=a2fcc519\" target=\"_blank\">http://us.focusrite.com/usb-audio-interfaces/scarlett-2i2</a>"},{"pid":"d50e518f4fc812855e79b4b26b6ada6485adb446","tid":600345,"uid":51396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a9f3f0a9d910a2a2571051014e4386cd3cb9170a","tid":600345,"uid":52539,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e415a04644ec8b5c3196b2320f2ce68e3859da2e","tid":600345,"uid":75448,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T13:59:30.000Z","msg":"你係咪唔滿意自已把聲"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T14:18:55.000Z","msg":"好似副歌d大聲位就有d刺耳 雖然冇爆音<br />\n已經較平衡左d聲 但都唔夠順耳<br />\n<br />\n但你話個聲底 都係 我覺得關軟件混音事?<br />\n聽日本cover d人把聲好暖 好立體"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T16:07:17.000Z","msg":"試下落EQ 同compressor<br />\ncompressor 主要幫你條track嘅大聲位壓低/ 細聲位拉大<br />\n另外唔同compressor plugin 有唔同聲底, 有D可以扮到&quot;暖聲&quot;<br />\n<br />\n同埋你個人同咪嘅距離, 有冇用pop filter, 都有影響"},{"pid":"1fbf1a433af816479c74977aa65e83f0df9c7edd","tid":600345,"uid":22748,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T04:59:27.000Z","msg":"用錄音咪錄返自己把聲，條track 係最raw ，同你平時自己唱k / 講野果陣直接自己聽返係好唔同的<br />\n<br />\n你錄完條track 就好似一塊未煮好既牛扒，要做一做mixing 先可以加強到厚d / 暖d既聲<br />\n<br />\n當然你本身聲底係點我就唔知<br />\n<br />\n千祈唔好用自己講野/唱k 聽到把聲做比較，你會好失望的"},{"pid":"c6025612b9af628125bb981decdea881a14803ea","tid":600345,"uid":26611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T07:24:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n錄音嘅話買個靚interface基本上係必須，尤其係做音樂嘢<br />\nInterface有mic pre會令你錄出嚟條聲比usb mic/普通3.5直插厚同warm同少noise（當然仲有好多因素 e.g. ADC 線材 等等）<br />\nSoftware方面PC都離不開Audition/Nuendo，Mac就Logic<br />\n專業嘅就用Pro Tools"}]}